{
  "stem": "2170.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the meantime, as we were waiting on the station, to the train should start to move, all of a sudden, the Russian two planes start to come in.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they start to bomb the station, right near as the bombs were falling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't care no more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Better to fall-- to die from a bomb than the dead that I saw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And somehow, in the middle-- in the morning, the train start to move.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went to Mogilev, which was a whole day, a whole night, almost half of a night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came into Mogilev, and we were looking for Jews or the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we came in, somebody told us that-- that Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Heshman's ?] hiding somewhere in-- in Mogilev.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I wanted to know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we came and they told us it's not there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did not have-- and we saw Germans all over, on the station, running already into Romania because the Russians were closing and closing closer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went back to the station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wanted to go back to Zhmerinka.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As we came in-- into the train, we-- we were in one of the wagons all alone by us, and then came in all of a sudden a Romanian conductor knocks into the door.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he comes in and he says, what are doing over here?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You are Jews?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're going back to-- he wanted to arrest us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he asked us if we have gold or we have something else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow I had a leather, a skin of leather in my-- in my-- all around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had breads and we had other things and we gave it him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he let us stay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't do nothing to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
